    <span class="kicker">Employee Productivity Tracking &amp; Intelligence</span>
    <h1>Your Data. Your Servers.<br><em>Total Productivity Visibility.</em></h1>
    <p class="lead">SmartEPT shows you who is present, who is productive, and who needs help — while every screenshot and activity log stays on <b>your own server</b>. Transparent, consent-based, and priced for Indian businesses.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/client/signup">Start 7-Day Free Trial →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://wa.me/919000098877?text=Hi%20Ametecs%2C%20I%20want%20a%20SmartEPT%20demo" target="_blank">Book a Demo on WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-chips">
      <span><b>Client-hosted</b> — data never leaves you</span>
      <span>From <b>₹29</b>/device/month</span>
      <span>By Ametecs — <b>300+</b> businesses</span>
    </div>
  </div>
