</header>

<!-- ================= USP ================= -->
<section class="usps">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="kicker">Why SmartEPT</span>
    <h2 class="sec">Three reasons teams choose us</h2>
    <div class="usp-grid">
      <div class="usp">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2.5l7.5 3v5.2c0 4.7-3.2 8.4-7.5 9.8-4.3-1.4-7.5-5.1-7.5-9.8V5.5L12 2.5Z"/><path d="M9 12l2.2 2.2L15.5 9.8"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Client data at client place</h3>
        <p>Screenshots, activity logs, camera events — everything is stored on <b>your server or your cloud</b>. Ametecs never holds your operational data unless you choose our managed cloud. Your infrastructure. Your data. Our intelligence.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="usp">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M9 8.5h6M9 11h6M9.4 8.5c3.1 0 4.7 1 4.7 2.6s-1.6 2.6-4.2 2.6H9.4l4.5 4.2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Honestly competitive pricing</h3>
        <p>From <b>₹29 per device per month</b> — priced per active device, not per employee. One PC shared by three shifts is still one licence. No hidden storage charges, no surprise invoices. GST invoice on everything.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="usp">
        <span class="tag-first">Industry First</span>
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 21V5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h8a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v16"/><path d="M3 21h18"/><path d="M18 21V9h1.5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v11"/><path d="M11 11.4v2.2"/></svg></div>
        <h3>Gate-to-PC unlock</h3>
        <p>The PC allows work <b>only after the employee punches at the gate</b>. No gate punch, no working desktop. Buddy punching, proxy attendance and ghost working end on day one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= GATE FEATURE ================= -->
<section class="gate" id="gate">
  <div class="gate-in">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker">Industry-First Feature</span>
      <h2>Punch at the gate.<br>Only then the PC works.</h2>
      <p>Every monitoring tool watches the computer. SmartEPT is the first to connect the <b style="color:#fff">office gate to the desktop</b>. Your biometric device and SmartEPT talk to each other — physical presence and digital work finally agree.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>No gate punch → the SmartEPT agent keeps the workstation on a polite lock screen</li>
        <li>Punch OUT at the gate mid-day → the PC auto-locks and an automatic break starts</li>
        <li>"In the building" vs "at the desk" reported separately — see hidden gaps</li>
        <li>Kills buddy punching, proxy attendance and ghost working — permanently</li>
        <li>Fail-safe by design: if the biometric device is down, admin override opens work instantly</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="flow">
      <div class="flow-step"><div class="n"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12a10 10 0 0 1 18-6"/><path d="M21.8 16c.2-2 .131-5.354 0-6"/><path d="M9 6.8a6 6 0 0 1 9 5.2v2"/><path d="M12 10a2 2 0 0 0-2 2c0 1.02-.1 2.51-.26 4"/><path d="M14 13.12c0 2.38 0 6.38-1 8.88"/><path d="M5 19.5C5.5 18 6 15 6 12a6 6 0 0 1 .34-2"/><path d="M8.65 22c.21-.66.45-1.32.57-2"/><path d="M2 16h.01"/></svg></div><div><b>1 · Employee punches at the gate</b><span>Biometric device sends the punch to SmartEPT in real time</span></div></div>
      <div class="flow-step"><div class="n"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 9.9-1"/></svg></div><div><b>2 · Their PC unlocks for work</b><span>SmartEPT agent verifies the gate event and allows the session</span></div></div>
      <div class="flow-step"><div class="n"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><line x1="10" y1="9" x2="10" y2="15"/><line x1="14" y1="9" x2="14" y2="15"/></svg></div><div><b>3 · Mid-day punch out? Auto-break</b><span>PC locks, break timer starts — resumes on punch-in</span></div></div>
      <div class="flow-step"><div class="n"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="10"/><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="16"/></svg></div><div><b>4 · Office-time vs desk-time report</b><span>Management sees the gap between present and productive</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= FEATURES ================= -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="kicker">Complete Platform</span>
    <h2 class="sec">Everything a manager needs, category by category</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub">Transparent and policy-based — employees always see a visible tracking status. No stealth mode, ever.</p>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><polyline points="12 7 12 12 15.5 14"/></svg></span>Attendance &amp; Shifts</h4><ul>
        <li>Automatic attendance from login / logout</li><li>Shift, late-login &amp; early-logout alerts</li>
        <li>Biometric device integration &amp; gate sync</li><li>Break tracking with auto-break on punch-out</li><li>Per-device biometric sync — live interval or fixed times</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"/></svg></span>Activity &amp; Productivity</h4><ul>
        <li>Active vs idle time, hour by hour</li><li>App &amp; website usage classification</li>
        <li>Productivity scoring (0–100) per employee</li><li>Team &amp; department comparisons</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M23 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4l2-3h6l2 3h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="4"/></svg></span>Screenshots &amp; Evidence</h4><ul>
        <li>Configurable screenshot schedules</li><li>Live screen view (Professional+)</li>
        <li>Screen recording (Enterprise / add-on)</li><li>Camera presence verification, where lawful</li><li>Screenshots pause instantly when the screen locks</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></span>Policy &amp; Compliance</h4><ul>
        <li>Website / application restrictions</li><li>USB &amp; file-transfer controls (Enterprise)</li>
        <li>Consent-first: policy shown before tracking</li><li>Immutable audit log of every sensitive access</li><li>Single active session per employee — force-logout any device</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"/><path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"/></svg></span>Reports &amp; Alerts</h4><ul>
        <li>Daily / weekly / monthly scheduled reports</li><li>Excessive-idle &amp; policy-violation alerts</li>
        <li>CSV / Excel exports for payroll</li><li>Role-based dashboards for every manager</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 8h13v5a5 5 0 0 1-5 5H9a5 5 0 0 1-5-5V8Z"/><path d="M17 9h2.2a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5H17"/><path d="M8 2.5v2M12 2.5v2"/></svg></span>Smart Breaks</h4><ul>
        <li>Lunch, Tea &amp; Other break categories</li><li>Per-company break-time limits you set</li>
        <li>Automatic reason capture when a break runs over</li><li>Manager review &amp; break report with excess time</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 20v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="3.2"/><path d="M22 20v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M15.5 3.6a4 4 0 0 1 0 6.8"/></svg></span>Meetings</h4><ul>
        <li>Schedule meetings with participants</li><li>Server-authorised join, auto-close at end</li>
        <li>Meeting time counts as productive — not idle</li><li>Dedicated meeting report</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><path d="M16.24 7.76a6 6 0 0 1 0 8.49M7.76 16.24a6 6 0 0 1 0-8.49M19.07 4.93a10 10 0 0 1 0 14.14M4.93 19.07a10 10 0 0 1 0-14.14"/></svg></span>Live Monitoring</h4><ul>
        <li>Live team presence — who's working right now</li><li>Instant idle on lock, sleep or display-off</li>
        <li>Live status refresh every few seconds</li><li>At-a-glance active vs idle board</li></ul></div>
      <div class="feat"><h4><span class="fi"><svg class="" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg></span>Integrations</h4><ul>
        <li>SmartPRS payroll &amp; attendance sync</li><li>SmartDCM agent-productivity link</li>
        <li>Biometric devices (eSSL &amp; more)</li><li>AD / SSO &amp; standard API (plan-based)</li></ul></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= PRICING ================= -->
<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div style="text-align:center"><span class="kicker">Simple, Transparent Pricing</span>
    <h2 class="sec">Pay per active device. Nothing hidden.</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub" style="margin:0 auto">One workstation used by multiple shifts = one licence. Web-only managers are free.</p></div>
    <div class="toggles">
      <div class="toggle" id="tgBill">
        <button data-v="quarterly" onclick="setBill('quarterly')">Quarterly</button>
        <button data-v="half_yearly" onclick="setBill('half_yearly')">Half-Yearly · 10% off</button>
        <button class="on" data-v="annual" onclick="setBill('annual')">Annual · save 25%</button>
      </div>
      <div class="toggle" id="tgHost">
        <button class="on" data-v="hosted" onclick="setHost('hosted')">Client-Hosted</button>
        <button data-v="cloud" onclick="setHost('cloud')">SmartEPT Cloud</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cloud-note" id="cloudNote">Prices per active device per month, billed annually, GST extra. You host the server — your data stays with you.</div>
    <div class="plans">
      <div class="plan">
        <h3>7-Day Trial</h3><div class="for">Full evaluation — up to 10 devices</div>
        <div class="price">₹0</div><div class="per">no card required</div>
        <ul>
          <li>All Professional features</li>
          <li>Up to 10 active devices</li>
          <li>5 GB cloud sandbox (optional)</li>
          <li>One admin + manager dashboard</li>
          <li class="no">No permanent free plan</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="/client/signup">Start Trial</a>
      </div>
      <div class="plan">
        <h3>Core</h3><div class="for">Small offices &amp; startups</div>
        <div class="price" data-plan="core">₹29<small> /device/mo</small></div><div class="per per-note"></div>
        <ul>
          <li>Attendance &amp; work-hour tracking</li>
          <li>Productivity classification</li>
          <li>Configurable screenshots</li>
          <li>Daily / weekly / monthly reports</li>
          <li>1 manager account</li>
          <li class="no">Live view &amp; restrictions</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="/client/signup?plan=core">Choose Core</a>
      </div>
      <div class="plan pop">
        <div class="pop-tag">MOST POPULAR</div>
        <h3>Professional</h3><div class="for">SMEs, call centres &amp; BPOs</div>
        <div class="price" data-plan="pro">₹59<small> /device/mo</small></div><div class="per per-note"></div>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything in Core</li>
          <li>Live status &amp; live screen view</li>
          <li>Website / app restrictions</li>
          <li>Productivity scoring &amp; comparisons</li>
          <li>Shift / idle / late-login alerts</li>
          <li>Multi-office + offline sync + API</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/client/signup?plan=professional">Choose Professional</a>
      </div>
      <div class="plan">
        <h3>Enterprise</h3><div class="for">Regulated &amp; complex organisations</div>
        <div class="price" data-plan="ent">₹99<small> /device/mo</small></div><div class="per per-note"></div>
        <ul>
          <li>Everything in Professional</li>
          <li>Screen recording &amp; camera presence</li>
          <li>USB / file-transfer controls</li>
          <li>AD / SSO &amp; advanced API</li>
          <li>Biometric + HRMS + payroll integrations</li>
          <li>Dedicated account manager</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="/client/signup?plan=enterprise">Choose Enterprise</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pr-foot">Minimum 10 devices or ₹499/month. Volume discounts from 26 devices. Perpetual licences available — <b>talk to sales</b>.<br>One-time <b>Setup &amp; Onboarding: ₹5,000</b> (covers up to 25 devices) + ₹100 per additional device — charged on your first invoice only.<br>SmartEPT Cloud adds storage rental at <b>₹3/GB/month</b> (first 500 GB · ₹2.50 to 2 TB · ₹2 above), minimum 50 GB.</div>

    <!-- CALCULATOR -->
    <div class="calc" id="calc">
      <div class="calc-grid">
        <div>
          <h3>What will it cost for your team?</h3>
          <div class="cs">Professional plan · annual billing · volume discount applied automatically.</div>
          <div class="devrow"><span style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink2)">Active devices</span><span class="devnum" id="devN">50</span></div>
          <input type="range" min="10" max="1000" step="5" value="50" id="devSlider" oninput="calc()">
          <div class="tier" id="tierNote"></div>
          <div class="calc-example" id="calcExample"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="calc-out">
          <div class="lbl" id="calcMode">Client-Hosted · Annual</div>
          <div class="big" id="calcMonthly">₹2,450</div>
          <div class="sm">per month</div>
          <hr>
          <div class="sm" style="font-size:15px"><b id="calcAnnual">₹29,400</b> per year + GST</div>
          <div class="sm" id="calcCloudLine" style="margin-top:6px"></div>
          <div class="sm" id="calcSetup" style="margin-top:8px;font-weight:700"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= COMPARE ================= -->
<section class="compare" id="cloud">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="kicker">Two Ways to Deploy</span>
    <h2 class="sec">Host it yourself, or let us manage it</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub">Both run the same SmartEPT. The difference is where the server lives and who maintains it.</p>
    <table class="cmp">
      <tr><th>What matters to you</th><th>Client-Hosted (recommended)</th><th>SmartEPT-Managed Cloud</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Where your data lives</td><td class="hl">Your server / your cloud — 100% with you</td><td>Ametecs-managed platform, contractual controls</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Licence price</td><td class="hl">Lowest — from ₹29/device/month</td><td>Client-hosted rate × 1.5</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Storage cost</td><td class="hl">Your own disk — free to you</td><td>₹3/GB/month, pay only for what you keep</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Server maintenance</td><td>Your IT team</td><td class="hl">Fully managed by Ametecs</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Backups &amp; monitoring</td><td>Your responsibility</td><td class="hl">Included in the 50% platform fee</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Setup time</td><td>Installed on your Windows server / Laragon stack</td><td class="hl">Same day — nothing to install centrally</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Best for</td><td>Cost-conscious teams with any IT support</td><td>Teams who want zero infrastructure worry</td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= ECOSYSTEM ================= -->
<section class="eco">
  <div class="wrap eco-in">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker">The Ametecs Ecosystem</span>
      <h3>Already using SmartDCM or SmartPRS?</h3>
      <p>SmartEPT plugs straight into your existing Ametecs products — attendance flows to SmartPRS payroll, productivity flows to SmartDCM incentives. And you get a standard 10% ecosystem discount on every plan and billing cycle.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="offer"><span>Existing SmartDCM / SmartPRS customers</span><b>10%<span style="font-size:14px;color:var(--ink3)"> off everything</span></b><span>every plan &amp; billing cycle · client-hosted or cloud</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= FAQ ================= -->
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:860px">
    <div style="text-align:center"><span class="kicker">Questions, Answered</span>
    <h2 class="sec">Frequently asked questions</h2></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">Where exactly is my employees' data stored?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>Under client-hosted deployment, the SmartEPT server runs on <b>your premises or your own cloud account</b> — every screenshot, activity log and camera event stays in your environment. Ametecs only keeps licence metadata (plan, device count, activation) needed to keep your product activated and updated. If you choose SmartEPT-managed cloud, we host the platform for you under contractual access, retention and deletion controls — and the data is still legally yours.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">How does the Gate-to-PC feature actually work?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>Your biometric gate device (eSSL and similar) pushes punches to SmartEPT. The SmartEPT agent on each PC checks: has this employee punched in at the gate today? If yes, the desktop session is allowed. If they punch out mid-day, the PC locks and an automatic break starts. If the biometric device ever goes down, an admin override opens work instantly — it is designed to never block your business.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">What counts as one licence — a device or an employee?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>An <b>active endpoint device</b>. One workstation used by three employees across shifts consumes just one licence — much better value for call centres and BPOs. Managers and admins who only use the web dashboard are free. Licences can be moved to a replacement device through controlled deactivation.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">How is SmartEPT Cloud storage billed?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>Separately and transparently: ₹3 per GB per month for the first 500 GB (₹2.50 to 2 TB, ₹2 above), minimum 50 GB. We measure your average daily usage and round up to the next GB. You control retention — data you delete stops being billed. Your licence and your storage always appear as two clear lines on the invoice.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">Is there a permanent free plan?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>No — and that's deliberate. You get a <b>7-day full-featured trial</b> for up to 10 devices (with an optional 5 GB cloud sandbox) to genuinely evaluate everything. After that, plans start at just ₹29 per device per month, so the entry price stays honest instead of hiding costs elsewhere.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">Is this legal? Do employees know they are tracked?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>SmartEPT is transparent by design — there is <b>no stealth mode</b>. The agent shows a visible tracking status and the active policy. Consent screens are shown where policy requires, and every access to sensitive data is written to an immutable audit log. You remain responsible for lawful deployment and employee communication, and we give you the tools to do it right.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">Can I buy it once instead of subscribing?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>Yes — perpetual licensing is available (per-device licence + central server licence, including the first 12 months of updates; AMC at 18% per year afterwards keeps updates and support active). Talk to sales for a perpetual quotation.</p></div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="fq(this)">What do setup, implementation and integrations cost?</button>
      <div class="faq-a"><p>A one-time <b>Setup &amp; Onboarding fee of ₹5,000</b> covers your first 25 devices (₹100 per additional device) — it includes installation assistance, configuration and go-live handholding, and appears only on your first invoice. Optional services are quoted separately: biometric integration from ₹15,000, HRMS/payroll or custom API integration from ₹25,000, white labelling from ₹1,00,000.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= CTA + LEAD ================= -->
<section class="cta" id="contact">
  <div class="wrap cta-in">
    <div>
      <span class="kicker">Get Started</span>
      <h2>See your team's real productivity this week.</h2>
      <p>Start the 7-day trial in minutes, or tell us about your team and we'll reply on WhatsApp with a tailored quote — usually within the hour.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/client/signup">Start 7-Day Free Trial →</a>
      <p style="margin-top:22px;font-size:14px">Prefer to talk? Call <b style="color:#fff" id="ctaPhone">+91 96666 12424</b> or email <b style="color:#fff" id="ctaEmail">sales@ametecsindia.com</b></p>
    </div>
    <form class="leadform" onsubmit="return sendWA(event)">
      <h3>Get a quote on WhatsApp</h3>
      <div class="fs">Fill this in — it opens WhatsApp with your details ready to send.</div>
      <label>Your name</label><input id="lfName" required placeholder="e.g. Rajesh Kumar">
      <label>Company</label><input id="lfCo" required placeholder="e.g. ABC Recoveries Pvt Ltd">
      <label>Your WhatsApp / mobile number</label><input id="lfPhone" required placeholder="e.g. 98480 12345" inputmode="tel" maxlength="16">
      <label>Number of devices</label>
      <select id="lfDev"><option>10–25</option><option>26–100</option><option>101–250</option><option>251–500</option><option>500+</option></select>
      <label>Interested in</label>
      <select id="lfPlan"><option>Professional (₹59) — Client-Hosted</option><option>Professional — SmartEPT Cloud</option><option>Core (₹29)</option><option>Enterprise (₹99)</option><option>Perpetual licence</option><option>Gate-to-PC feature demo</option></select>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Send on WhatsApp →</button>
      <div class="wa-note">Opens wa.me — Ametecs sales · 90000 98877</div>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= FOOTER ================= -->
<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="foot-grid">
      <div class="foot-logo">
        <img src="/img/smartept-logo-h-dark.png" alt="SmartEPT by Ametecs">
        <p>Employee Productivity Tracking &amp; Intelligence System.<br>Empowering Productivity. Simplifying Management.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h5>Product</h5>
        <ul><li><a href="#features">Features</a></li><li><a href="#gate">Gate-to-PC</a></li><li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li><li><a href="#cloud">Cloud vs Hosted</a></li><li><a href="/client">Client Login</a></li><li><a href="/admin">Admin Login</a></li></ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h5>Legal</h5>
        <ul><li><a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></li><li><a href="/refunds">Refund Policy</a></li><li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li></ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h5>Ecosystem</h5>
        <ul><li>SmartDCM — Debt Collection CRM</li><li>SmartPRS — HRM &amp; Payroll</li><li>SmartEPT — Productivity</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h5>Ametecs India Private Limited</h5>
        <p>Modern Profound Techpark, Ground Floor, Hive Space, opp. Google, Whitefields, Kondapur, Hyderabad, Telangana 500084<br>GST: 36AAHCT0971F1ZB<br>Phone: +91 96666 12424 · Email: sales@ametecsindia.com<br>WhatsApp: 90000 98877</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="foot-base">
      <span>© 2026 Ametecs India Private Limited. All rights reserved.</span>
      <span>Transparent · Consent-based · Policy-driven — never stealth software.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
/* ===== mobile nav ===== */
(function(){
  var links=document.getElementById('navLinks'), h=document.getElementById('navToggle');
  if(!links||!h) return;
  function shut(){ links.classList.remove('openm'); h.setAttribute('aria-expanded','false'); }
  h.addEventListener('click', function(e){ e.stopPropagation(); var o=links.classList.toggle('openm'); h.setAttribute('aria-expanded', o?'true':'false'); });
  Array.prototype.forEach.call(links.querySelectorAll('a'), function(a){ a.addEventListener('click', shut); });
  document.addEventListener('click', function(e){ if(links.classList.contains('openm') && !links.contains(e.target) && !h.contains(e.target)) shut(); });
  window.addEventListener('resize', function(){ if(window.innerWidth>960) shut(); });
})();
/* ===== pricing toggles ===== */
/* Built-in rates are the FALLBACK; live rates load from /api/v1/public/plans
   (edit a plan in /admin → Plans and this page follows within 5 minutes). */
let RATES = { core:{annual:29,monthly:39}, pro:{annual:59,monthly:79}, ent:{annual:99,monthly:129} };
let TIERS = [[25,59],[100,49],[250,39],[500,29],[1000,24],[Infinity,20]];
let SETUP = { base:5000, included:25, per:100 };
let CLOUD_X = 1.5, STOR_RATE = 3, STOR_MIN_GB = 50, STOR_MIN_INR = 150, ANN_DISC = 0.25, HALF_DISC = 0.10;
let bill='annual', host='hosted';
function fmt(n){ return '₹' + n.toLocaleString('en-IN'); }
function planPrice(k){ const A = RATES[k].annual; let r = bill==='quarterly' ? Math.round(A/(1-ANN_DISC)) : bill==='half_yearly' ? Math.round(A/(1-ANN_DISC)*(1-HALF_DISC)) : A; if(host==='cloud') r = Math.round(r*CLOUD_X); return r; }
function setBill(v){ bill=v; syncToggles(); render(); calc(); }
function setHost(v){ host=v; syncToggles(); render(); calc(); }
function syncToggles(){
  document.querySelectorAll('#tgBill button').forEach(b=>b.classList.toggle('on',b.dataset.v===bill));
  document.querySelectorAll('#tgHost button').forEach(b=>b.classList.toggle('on',b.dataset.v===host));
}
function render(){
  document.querySelector('[data-plan=core]').innerHTML = fmt(planPrice('core'))+'<small> /device/mo</small>';
  document.querySelector('[data-plan=pro]').innerHTML  = fmt(planPrice('pro')) +'<small> /device/mo</small>';
  document.querySelector('[data-plan=ent]').innerHTML  = fmt(planPrice('ent')) +'<small> /device/mo</small>';
  const notes = document.querySelectorAll('.per-note');
  notes.forEach(n=>n.textContent = host==='cloud' ? ('+ storage from ₹'+STOR_RATE+'/GB/mo') : ({quarterly:'billed quarterly',half_yearly:'✓ save '+Math.round(HALF_DISC*100)+'% vs quarterly',annual:'✓ save '+Math.round(ANN_DISC*100)+'% vs quarterly'}[bill]));
  document.getElementById('cloudNote').textContent = host==='cloud'
    ? ('SmartEPT Cloud = client-hosted rate × '+CLOUD_X+' (managed hosting, monitoring, backup) + storage rental ₹'+STOR_RATE+'/GB/month. GST extra.')
    : 'Prices per active device per month, ' + ({quarterly:'billed quarterly',half_yearly:'billed half-yearly',annual:'billed annually'}[bill]) + ', GST extra. You host the server — your data stays with you.';
  calc();
}
/* ===== calculator (Professional, volume tiers on annual) ===== */
function tierRate(d){ for (const [max, rate] of TIERS) if (d <= max) return rate; return TIERS[TIERS.length-1][1]; }
function tierIdx(d){ for (let i=0;i<TIERS.length;i++) if (d <= TIERS[i][0]) return i; return TIERS.length-1; }
const TIER_NAMES = ['Standard public price','SME volume rate','Mid-market rate','Large operation rate','Enterprise volume rate','Custom contract'];
function tierName(d){ return TIER_NAMES[Math.min(tierIdx(d), TIER_NAMES.length-1)]; }
function calc(){
  const d = +document.getElementById('devSlider').value;
  document.getElementById('devN').textContent = d;
  const cycleLbl = bill==='quarterly'?'Quarterly':bill==='half_yearly'?'Half-Yearly':'Annual';
  let tRate = tierRate(d);
  let rate = bill==='quarterly' ? Math.round(tRate/(1-ANN_DISC)) : bill==='half_yearly' ? Math.round(tRate/(1-ANN_DISC)*(1-HALF_DISC)) : tRate;
  let cloud = host==='cloud';
  let r = cloud ? Math.round(rate*CLOUD_X) : rate;
  let monthly = d*r;
  let storGB = Math.max(STOR_MIN_GB, Math.ceil(d*2));           // rough 2 GB/device estimate
  let storCost = cloud ? Math.max(STOR_MIN_INR, Math.round(storGB*STOR_RATE)) : 0;
  document.getElementById('calcMode').textContent = (cloud?'SmartEPT Cloud':'Client-Hosted')+' · '+cycleLbl+' · Professional';
  document.getElementById('calcMonthly').textContent = fmt(monthly + storCost);
  document.getElementById('calcAnnual').textContent = fmt((monthly+storCost)*12);
  document.getElementById('calcCloudLine').textContent = cloud ? `= ${d} × ${fmt(r)} licence + ~${storGB} GB × ₹${STOR_RATE} storage` : 'Storage on your own server — ₹0 to us';
  let setup = SETUP.base + Math.max(0, d-SETUP.included)*SETUP.per;
  document.getElementById('calcSetup').textContent = `+ one-time setup & onboarding ${fmt(setup)} (first invoice only)`;
  document.getElementById('tierNote').innerHTML = `Volume tier: <b>${tierName(d)} — ${fmt(r)}/device/mo</b> (${cycleLbl.toLowerCase()}${cloud?', cloud':''})`;
  document.getElementById('calcExample').innerHTML = `<b>Worked example:</b> ${d} devices × ${fmt(r)} = <b>${fmt(monthly)}/month</b>${cloud?` + ~${fmt(storCost)} storage = <b>${fmt(monthly+storCost)}/month</b>`:''} → ${fmt((monthly+storCost)*12)}/year + one-time setup ${fmt(setup)} + GST.`;
  
}
/* ===== FAQ ===== */
function fq(btn){
  const item = btn.parentElement, a = item.querySelector('.faq-a'), open = item.classList.contains('open');
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item.open').forEach(i=>{i.classList.remove('open');i.querySelector('.faq-a').style.maxHeight=null;});
  if(!open){ item.classList.add('open'); a.style.maxHeight = a.scrollHeight+'px'; }
}
/* ===== WhatsApp lead ===== */
function sendWA(e){
  e.preventDefault();
  const name=document.getElementById('lfName').value, co=document.getElementById('lfCo').value,
        ph=document.getElementById('lfPhone').value, dev=document.getElementById('lfDev').value,
        plan=document.getElementById('lfPlan').value;
  const msg = `Hi Ametecs, I'm ${name} from ${co}. We have ${dev} devices and we're interested in SmartEPT — ${plan}. Please send a quote.`;
  /* Real lead capture (blueprint §5): the enquiry also lands in /admin → Leads
     with an instant email to sales — fire-and-forget, never blocks WhatsApp. */
  if (location.protocol !== 'file:') {
    try { fetch('/api/v1/public/leads', {method:'POST', headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json','Accept':'application/json'},
      body: JSON.stringify({name:name, company:co, phone:ph,
        devices_interested: parseInt(dev,10)||null, message:'Interested in: '+plan+' ('+dev+' devices)', source:'website'})}).catch(()=>{}); } catch(err){}
  }
  window.open((window.WA_BASE||'https://wa.me/919000098877')+'?text='+encodeURIComponent(msg),'_blank');
  return false;
}
/* ===== LIVE PRICES from SmartEPT Central =====
   Edit a plan in /admin → Plans and this page updates automatically
   (cached 5 min). If the API is unreachable the built-in rates above stand. */
(function liveRates(){
  if (location.protocol === 'file:') return; // offline preview keeps fallback rates
  fetch('/api/v1/public/plans', {headers:{Accept:'application/json'}})
    .then(r => r.ok ? r.json() : null)
    .then(d => {
      if (!d || !d.plans || !d.plans.length) return;
      const map = {core:'core', professional:'pro', enterprise:'ent'};
      d.plans.forEach(p => { const k = map[p.code]; if (k) RATES[k] = {annual:+p.inr_annual, monthly:+p.inr_monthly}; });
      const pro = d.plans.find(p => p.code === 'professional');
      if (pro && pro.volume_tiers && pro.volume_tiers.length)
        TIERS = pro.volume_tiers.map(t => [t.max === null ? Infinity : +t.max, +t.rate]);
      if (d.setup) SETUP = {base:+d.setup.base, included:+d.setup.included, per:+d.setup.per_extra};
      if (d.cloud_multiplier) CLOUD_X = +d.cloud_multiplier;
      if (d.cycles) { if (d.cycles.annual_discount!=null) ANN_DISC = +d.cycles.annual_discount; if (d.cycles.half_yearly_discount!=null) HALF_DISC = +d.cycles.half_yearly_discount; }
      if (d.storage) { if (d.storage.slabs && d.storage.slabs.length) STOR_RATE = +d.storage.slabs[0][2]; if (d.storage.min_gb!=null) STOR_MIN_GB = +d.storage.min_gb; if (d.storage.min_inr!=null) STOR_MIN_INR = +d.storage.min_inr; }
      render();
    })
    .catch(() => {});
})();

/* ===== CMS-EDITABLE CONTENT from SmartEPT Central (blueprint §5) =====
   Super Admin edits hero text, announcement bar, contact details and
   testimonials in /admin → Landing CMS. Empty values keep this page's
   built-in copy — offline/file:// preview is untouched. */
(function cmsContent(){
  if (location.protocol === 'file:') return;
  fetch('/api/v1/public/content', {headers:{Accept:'application/json'}})
    .then(r => r.ok ? r.json() : null)
    .then(c => {
      if (!c) return;
      const heroH1 = document.querySelector('.hero-in h1');
      const heroLead = document.querySelector('.hero-in .lead');
      if (c.landing_hero_title && heroH1) heroH1.textContent = c.landing_hero_title;
      if (c.landing_hero_subtitle && heroLead) heroLead.textContent = c.landing_hero_subtitle;
      if (c.landing_contact_phone) { const el = document.getElementById('ctaPhone'); if (el) el.textContent = c.landing_contact_phone; }
      if (c.landing_contact_email) { const el = document.getElementById('ctaEmail'); if (el) el.textContent = c.landing_contact_email; }
      if (c.whatsapp_number && /^[0-9]{10,14}$/.test(c.whatsapp_number)) window.WA_BASE = 'https://wa.me/' + c.whatsapp_number;
      if (c.landing_announcement) {
        const bar = document.createElement('div');
        bar.style.cssText = 'background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0E7C8F,#1899AE);color:#fff;text-align:center;padding:9px 16px;font:600 13.5px Inter,\'Segoe UI\',sans-serif;letter-spacing:.2px';
        bar.textContent = c.landing_announcement;
        document.body.insertBefore(bar, document.body.firstChild);
      }
      if (Array.isArray(c.landing_testimonials) && c.landing_testimonials.length) {
        const cta = document.getElementById('contact');
        if (cta) {
          const sec = document.createElement('section');
          sec.style.cssText = 'padding:64px 0;background:#FFFFFF';
          sec.innerHTML = '<div class="wrap"><h2 style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:28px">What our customers say</h2>'
            + '<div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));gap:18px">'
            + c.landing_testimonials.slice(0,4).map(function(t){
                return '<div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid #E7E9EF;border-radius:14px;padding:20px 22px">'
                  + '<p style="font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#3A4150">&ldquo;' + String(t.quote||'').replace(/</g,'&lt;') + '&rdquo;</p>'
                  + '<p style="margin-top:12px;font-weight:800;color:#0B6373;font-size:13px">' + String(t.name||'').replace(/</g,'&lt;')
                  + '</p><p style="font-size:12px;color:#878C99">' + String(t.role||'').replace(/</g,'&lt;') + '</p></div>';
              }).join('')
            + '</div></div>';
          cta.parentNode.insertBefore(sec, cta);
        }
      }
    })
    .catch(() => {});
})();
render();
</script>
</body>
</html>
